<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>택배예약 - GS Retail</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
	<script src="../../js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<div class="skipMenu"><a href="#container">본문 바로가기</a></div>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<header class="header">
			<h1>택배예약</h1>
			<a href="#" class="btnBack">이전 페이지 이동</a>
			<button type="button" id="qrpop" class="btnQr" title="QR코드 팝업 열기">QR코드</button>
		</header>
		<!-- //header -->
		<section id="container" class="content">
            <!-- 내용 -->
			<div class="tabArea">
				<ul role="tablist">
					<li><a href="#" role="tab" aria-selected="false">예약확인/취소</a></li>
					<li><a href="#" role="tab" aria-selected="true">이용안내</a></li>
					<li><a href="#" role="tab" aria-selected="false">운임안내</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div class="tabCont">
				<div class="postboxIntro">
					<h2 class="introTit"><span class="bg">Postbox</span><br> 택배서비스란?</h2>
					<p class="introTxt">Postbox는 저울이 달린 무인택배장비로 저렴한 운임과 신뢰할 수 있는 택배 서비스를 이용할 수 있습니다.</p>
					<ul class="introSrv">
						<li><span>최저운임</span><em>2,600원</em></li>
						<li><span>신뢰할수있는</span><em>무게별운임</em></li>
						<li><span>회원/비회원</span><em>누구나</em></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="conBlock line">
					<h2 class="titDep1">Postbox 이용절차</h2>
					<ol class="stepList">
						<li>
							<em class="step">STEP <span class="no">01</span></em>
							<div class="con"><strong class="sTit">접수</strong><p class="sTxt">(비회원접수/회원접수)</p></div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<em class="step">STEP <span class="no">02</span></em>
							<div class="con"><strong class="sTit">중량측정</strong></div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<em class="step">STEP <span class="no">03</span></em>
							<div class="con"><strong class="sTit">상품 종류 선택</strong></div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<em class="step">STEP <span class="no">04</span></em>
							<div class="con"><strong class="sTit">정보입력</strong><p class="sTxt">(송/수화인 정보입력)</p></div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<em class="step">STEP <span class="no">05</span></em>
							<div class="con"><strong class="sTit">운임확인</strong><p class="sTxt">(선/착불 선택)</p></div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<em class="step">STEP <span class="no">05</span></em>
							<div class="con"><strong class="sTit">운송장 출력</strong></div>
						</li>
					</ol>
				</div>
				<div class="conBlock line">
					<h2 class="titDep1">회원 혜택</h2>
					<ul class="srvList srvDelivery02">
						<li><strong class="srvTit">이용의 편리성</strong><p class="srvTxt">365일 24시간 가까운 GS25, GS THE FRESH, lalavla  접수처에서 택배 발송 업무가 가능하며 온라인 택배 예약을 통해 편리하게 발송 할 수 있습니다.</p></li>
						<li><strong class="srvTit">합리적인 운임</strong><p class="srvTxt">그램단위까지 측정하여 최저 2,600원부터 중량별로 운임신청</p></li>
						<li><strong class="srvTit">SMS 서비스</strong><p class="srvTxt">접수시점부터 배달완료까지 배송단계별로 SMS서비스를 제공</p></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="btnFixed">
                    <div class="btnPrss">
                        <button type="button" class="btnTP active">확인</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
			</div>
            <!--//내용 -->
		</section>
		<!-- //container -->
	</div>
	<!-- //wrapper -->
</body>
</html>

